What a clever trick indeed.

16
00:01:11,712 --> 00:01:12,630
The medicinal properties

17
00:01:12,639 --> 00:01:14,239
of the pear soup and the fragrance

18
00:01:14,239 --> 00:01:15,160
from this box clash.

19
00:01:15,360 --> 00:01:16,680
If one doesn't know pharmacology,

20
00:01:16,680 --> 00:01:18,144
