21
00:01:19,400 --> 00:01:21,120
The poisoner is truly cunning.

22
00:01:24,800 --> 00:01:26,160
(Could it really be Auntie?)

23
00:01:36,190 --> 00:01:37,376
The poison has been neutralized.

24
00:01:37,839 --> 00:01:39,440
Thanks to Physician Su's Yulu Pills.

25
00:01:39,480 --> 00:01:41,239
Or else, he will be in danger.

26
00:01:48,160 --> 00:01:49,319
I frightened you last night.

27
00:01:49,959 --> 00:01:50,760
It's okay.

28
00:02:02,599 --> 00:02:04,879
I narrowly escaped
a fire many years ago.

29
00:02:05,680 --> 00:02:06,919
Seeing candles

30
00:02:08,479 --> 00:02:10,199
reminds me of that fire.

31
00:02:11,919 --> 00:02:12,720
I'm sorry.

32
00:02:14,360 --> 00:02:16,279
Something wrong
with the food box Auntie sent.

33
00:02:17,080 --> 00:02:18,080
Perhaps there's

34
00:02:18,279 --> 00:02:19,479
some misunderstanding...

35
00:02:20,520 --> 00:02:21,559
I'll go ask her to clarify.

36
00:02:22,279 --> 00:02:23,080
Shu'er.

37
00:02:24,360 --> 00:02:26,320
Do you really think
this is a misunderstanding?

38
00:02:27,550 --> 00:02:29,216
Whether it's a misunderstanding or not,

39
00:02:29,720 --> 00:02:31,000
I need to find out for sure.

40
00:02:31,919 --> 00:02:33,039
Rest well first.

41
00:02:50,720 --> 00:02:51,800
Shu'er,

42
00:02:51,919 --> 00:02:52,759
