and was carried back to his room.

121
00:09:36,039 --> 00:09:36,960
I need to go check.

122
00:09:36,960 --> 00:09:38,119
What can you do there?

123
00:09:38,400 --> 00:09:38,960
Don't go.

124
00:09:39,440 --> 00:09:40,200
Go to chop wood.

125
00:09:40,200 --> 00:09:41,919
Who chops wood at night?

126
00:09:41,919 --> 00:09:42,679
Let's go! Hurry up!

127
00:09:43,200 --> 00:09:44,239
Don't pull me.

128
00:09:55,000 --> 00:09:55,760
Don't go.

129
00:09:58,640 --> 00:09:59,119
Okay.

130
00:09:59,119 --> 00:10:00,119
I'll stay here.

131
00:10:01,000 --> 00:10:01,919
Sleep peacefully.

